OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine in
OL,7,Fplaces. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be dry with variable amounts of
OL,9,Fcloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,12,Fvariable amounts of cloud and sunny
OL,13,Fspells, best of the sunshine later on.
OL,14,FBecoming very warm, especially in the
OL,15,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
