OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly dry, settled and becoming very
OL,7,Fwarm or hot on Thursday and Friday
OL,8,Fwith plenty of sunshine although the
OL,9,Feast coast may see haar later Friday.
OL,10,FDry, largely cloudy Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
